name: Rowan University
description: This is a map of Rowan University's Glassboro Campus.

properties.name: Robinson Hall
properties.description: This is Robinson Hall, home to many departments on campus, including the department of Geography and Environment.

properties.name: Rowan Boulevard Apartments
properties.description: These are the newer on-campus apartments.  I lived here last year.  I would not recommend living here again.

properties.name: Rowan Hall
properties.description: This building is home to the department of Engineering.  There is also a lovely pond behind this building, which is a great place to go sit in peace and quiet and read a book.

properties.name: Loop around Campus
properties.description: This is a 2.2 mile loop around campus, which I frequently run.
